snippet.title: Swords of Gurrah - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Out Now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/833090/Swords_of_Gurrah/

Official Discord: https://discord.gg/ZDPgK5

Swords of Gurrah is a game changing Online PVP sword fighting Virtual reality experience that utilized a unique swordplay system based around blades shattering on impact and regenerating. This provides a epic and unique combat system that will bring the VR sword fighting experience to the next level!

Get ready for great replayability with many weapons, gamemodes, and singleplayer/ Co-op content!
